features: 【Pet-Friendly Barking Control Device】 The automatic anti bark device uses the latest ultrasonic technology which is suitable for dogs of all breeds and Most of sizes. Stop excessive, noisy dog barking by emitting an ultrasonic sound to silence the dog.Anti barking device with three adjustable ultrasonic volume, low, medium, and high,Please turn the knob to test different frequency bands to obtain the best results.

【30FT Dog Barking Deterrent Range】 Ultrasonic anti barking device with 3 distance level ranges up to 3Ft. Simply put this dog bark control machine in any outdoor setting where excessive barking occurs. The Unit will automatically detect dog’s barking sounds and emit a safe ultrasonic sound that only dogs can hear to deter and train your or yours NEIGHBOUR’s dog to stop barking!Doorbell no more!

【 Easily use anti barking device with royal service】The barking control device with LED indicator can help you understand device on working or battery low. When working on 3 differen levels, the light will flash red every 6s; the Blue light stays on 3s when the sonic bark deterrent is triggered by barking; the Blue light will flash when in low power. Any problem with our anti barking device, please feel free to contact us, we will reply within 24 hours.

【Using outdoor and indoor】 The humane stop dog barking devices with IP4 Rainproof function and the portable hook are suitable for use outdoors, and easy to hang on trees, walls, or fence posts. This Ultrasonic dog barking control device can save space or be set on a desk, wall, and shelf higher than 1.5m indoors, which can make it more effective to avoid barking, digging, fighting, etc. Our anti barking device can be set outdoor to stop homeless dog barking.

【Warm Tips for Sonic Bark Deterrents】Anti Barking Device is not applicable to the following situations: aggressive dogs, noisy surroundings, hearing impaired dogs, more dogs together, dogs under 6 months or over 8 years. If you find that the dog does not meet the above conditions, Please do not return the Anti barking Device training tool immediately, as the dog will need time to get used to the dog barking control devices, for up to two weeks.
description: Product description Product description Here's our Ultrasonic Dog Trainer - the go-to tool for those seeking serenity and tranquility, whether you're Trip, Night Working People,Lady,Student and Many Special People. This handy device is packed with features to help you tame your pet's behavior in no time. How to Use 1. Lightening Mode: Just slide the switch to the Light icon and hit the ON button on top. Simple as that! 2. Dog Training Mode: Slide the switch to position 1 and press ON. Then, aim the trainer straight at your pup from about 6 feet away (it works up to 20 feet). Give a clear command, and press the button for a second or two. Repeat until your pet gets it. 3. Chasing Dog Mode: Slide the switch to position 2 and press ON. Use the same method as Dog Training Mode to keep unwanted dogs at bay. Tips Distance is Key: Don't get too close or too far. The 6-20 feet range is perfect for getting your pet's attention. Consistency Counts: Remember, training is a two-way street. Be consistent with your commands and positive reinforcement. Keep it Safe: Always point the trainer away from your eyes or ears, and never use it on humans. Battery Life: Make sure to check the battery regularly and replace it when needed. Don't Overdo It: Like any training tool, don't overuse it. Your pet needs time to process and respond.Package Anti Barking Device*1 User manual*1 So, whether you're at home or on the road, trust our Ultrasonic Dog Trainer to make your life a little more peaceful and your pet a little more obedient!
